snippet.title: Spellzone Game Trailer (ver. 1.2)
snippet.description:
Game footages comes from patch 1.1I, available downloads are in 1.1H version, check the discord for further updates! Also it would be nice if you subscribe, like and share this video with others. Thank you in advance, best regards, Soulrender.

Download from Itch.io - https://soulrender.itch.io/spellzone
Download from Indiexpo.net* - https://www.indiexpo.net/pl/games/starcatcher-online-demo
Download from Rpgmaker.net - https://rpgmaker.net/games/12240/
* - Since indiexpo.net does not allow to edit links, game remains on that portal on it's code name "Star Catcher"

The trailer synopsis was written by Rpgmaker forum user, ThreeSixNine - https://forums.rpgmakerweb.com/index.php?members/threesixnine.136073/

Forum discussion: https://forums.rpgmakerweb.com/index.php?threads/spellzone.139621/unread
Discord Server: https://discord.gg/v5sYjFaQ.

Resources used for the trailer:
- Video clips found on Pixabay:
* Felipe David
* Lay-Z Owl
* Cesar Ramirez V Traphitho
And on shutterstock.com

Music provided by HearWeGo (https://goo.gl/nDS3zR)
Artist: MOON
Title: Hope
Listen on YouTube: https://youtu.be/cVog-tfTjY8
